    {
        "content": "<p>After some digging, I'm dependent on a notation for <code>$&gt;</code> that used to be in Lean 3, tagged to <code>functor.map_const_rev</code> that used to be in <code>init.control.functor</code> &amp; this is used all over the place in <code>mathlib</code></p>",
        "id": 313375851,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928299
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>ok so add it like <code>infix \" $&gt; \" =&gt; Functor.mapConstRev</code></p>",
        "id": 313375934,
        "sender_full_name": "Mario Carneiro",
        "timestamp": 1669928335
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>which is also missing.</p>",
        "id": 313376276,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928436
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>pretty trivial to def tho.</p>",
        "id": 313376314,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928451
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Should we add it to <code>mathlib</code>, or upstream?</p>",
        "id": 313376368,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928464
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Looks like <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"307953\">@Ruben Van de Velde</span>  did this in place.</p>",
        "id": 313376917,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928648
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, should still move it somewhere, probably. Let's keep it in mathlib, though</p>",
        "id": 313376980,
        "sender_full_name": "Ruben Van de Velde",
        "timestamp": 1669928675
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Probably should move to <code>Control.Functor</code>, yeah?</p>",
        "id": 313377160,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928744
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think we also want the notation, or else lots of downstream stuff in <code>mathlib</code> will break.</p>",
        "id": 313377367,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928812
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'll do a mini-PR for this...</p>",
        "id": 313377441,
        "sender_full_name": "Arien Malec",
        "timestamp": 1669928838
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I also moved it in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/803\">mathlib4#803</a>, but feel free to do it separately if you prefer</p>",
        "id": 313377723,
